werbalowsky and irwin gold began assembling what would become an active dominant worldwide financial restructuring group with the surge of mergers acquisitions and leveraged buyouts wall street’s large investment banking firms began calling on houlihan lokey for independent valuation expertise in fairness solvency and employee stock ownership plan esop opinions the firm advised on transactions valued at more than  billion during this period the firm also started to offer estate planning valuation services in addition the firm opened several offices in the s in new york city san francisco and chicago sedit houlihan lokey opened eight offices across the us in the s and s as it expanded in  to grow its information services division houlihan lokey acquired mergerstat a publishing company with a year history in analytical ma research from merrill lynch sedit in  houlihan lokey launched its first nonus office by expanding into london it also expanded its industry group platform and private equity coverage program in keeping with investment banking trends in  houlihan lokey advised the official creditors committees in three large bankruptcies worldcom enron and conseco in  the firm opened a paris office in  the firm opened a frankfurt office also in  houlihan lokey agreed to merge with orix usa the us corporate lending operations of orix corp of japan to address the growing international demand for middlemarket investment banking services in  houlihan lokey expanded into asia opening offices in hong kong and tokyo within the next three years the firm also opened an office in beijing in  houlihan lokey advised the creditors of lehman brothers sedit in  houlihan lokey bought a sizable minority stake in avista advisory group a then decadeold advisory group this gave the firm offices in both mumbai and singapore in  houlihan lokey expanded its financial institutions group through the acquisition of milestone advisors the firm also launched the illiquid financial assets practice to advise on the sales of assets such as stakes in loan pools life settlements minority positions pharmaceutical royalties and operating leases in  houlihan lokey strengthened its capabilities and coverage for clients across the technology sector with the acquisition of archpoint partners in  houlihan lokey acquired management consulting firm bridge strategy group digital media and entertainment focused investment bank mesa securities londonbased consumerfocused firm mcqueen ltd and operations of the continental european investment bank leonardo  co also in  houlihan lokey acquired the investment banking operations of leonardo  co nv in germany the netherlands and spain and became a minority partner in a joint venture with the management team of leonardo in respect to leonardo’s investment banking operations in italy this gave the firm offices in both rome and milan on august   houlihan lokey completed its initial public offering beginning trading as hli on the nyse in january  houlihan lokey acquired black stone ip a leader in techip advisory work operationsedit financial restructuringedit the financial restructuring team has approximately  professionals worldwide and every assignment is staffed with professionals who facilitate the completion of due diligence and analysis houlihan lokey has advised several extremely complicated deals and between  and  the firm advised on more than  restructuring transactions with aggregate debt claims in excess of  trillion including the five largest of all time lehman brothers washington mutual worldcom general motors and cit group corporate financeedit corporate finance is best known for offering mergers  acquisitions and capital markets advisory services the firm has advised public and private institutions on buyside and sellside transactions as well as leveraged loans private mezzanine debt highyield debt ipos followons convertibles pipes private equity and liability management transactions the company has also developed an expertise in advising financial sponsors on all types of transactions effectively creating one of the largest financial sponsors groups on wall street financial advisory servicesedit this division offers opinion services transaction  valuation reporting services real estate valuation  advisory portfolio valuation and financial consulting to company owners managers and special committees in their interactions with auditors and regulators strategic consultingedit this division helps clients learn their options for delivering greater shareholder value identify and capitalize on opportunities outside of traditional business models find operating efficiencies and accelerate profitable growth and uncover possible strategic alliances that enhance gotomarket strategies rankings and awardsedit  rankings and awards • restructuring deal of the year for africa – edcon—the bankers deals of the year  • restructuring deal of the year for the americas – sandridge energy—the bankers deals of the year •  • restructuring deal of the year for asiapacific – kaisa—the bankers deals of the year  • restructuring deal of the year for europe – codere—the bankers deals of the year   rankings and awards • restructuring deal of the year for asiapacific – pt berlian laju tanker tbk—the bankers deals of the year  • restructuring deal of the year for the americas – indiana toll road—the bankers deals of the year  • most innovative investment bank for restructuring—the bankers  investment banking awards  rankings and awards • best loan restructuring house—globalcapital syndicated loan leveraged finance and private placement awards • grand prix restructuring deal of the year for large cap – vivarte—le magazine des affaires  • cross border deal of the year for usasia region – ldk solar—the ma advisors international ma awards • cross border deal of the year over  billion – ldk solar—the ma advisors turnaround awards • restructuring deal of the year for asiapacific – mirabela nickel—the bankers deals of the year  • restructuring deal of the year for europe – punch taverns—the bankers deals of the year   rankings and awards • the banker’s  restructuring deals of the year awards americas american airlines • tma europe turnaround of the year awards  large company award solarworld ag • globalcapital’s best loan restructuring advisor   rankings and awards • no  global restructuring advisor — thomson reuters • no  us ma fairness opinion advisor over the past  years — thomson reuters • no  ma advisor for us transactions under  billion — thomson reuters • restructuring advisor of the year — international financing review ifr • best loan restructuring house — euroweek • european restructuring house of the year — financial news • dealmaker of the year bta bank  billion restructuring — finance monthly • crossborder dealmaker of the year for eurodrip — acquisition internationals  ma awards • restructuring winner europe for eircom — the bankers deals of the year  • restructuring winner africa for afrisam — the bankers deals of the year  • restructuring winner americas for kerzner international — the bankers deals of the year  in  vaultcom named houlihan lokey the best bank to work for being ranked first in compensation selectivity diversity hours training employee satisfaction business outlook and culture also in  houlihan lokey was named international financing reviews european restructuring house industriesedit houlihan lokey bankers focus on industries that include aerospace building products business services chemicals consumer products defense and government services energy financial institutions healthcare industrial  environmental technologies industrials automotive infrastructure services  construction lodging  leisure materials engineering media metals plastics  packaging real estate retail  food sports  entertainment technology telecommunications and transportation  logistics office locationsedit amsterdam atlanta beijing chicago dallas frankfurt hong kong houston london los angeles madrid miami milan minneapolis mumbai newport beach new york city paris rome san francisco singapore sydney tokyo washington dc notes and referencesedit  vincent roger energy cells help power century city skyscraper los angeles times february   retrieved february     houlihan lokey retrieved december   registered office   century park west los angeles ca  united states  a b houlihan lokey about us retrieved june     httpwwwhlcomemailpdffactsfigureshoulihanlokeyfactsfigurespdf  httpswwwreuterscomarticlelehmanfeesiduslemea  houlihan unveils indian partnership wwwhlcom retrieved    houlihan lokey significantly expands financial services coverage with acquisition of milestone advisors llc wwwhlcom retrieved    willmer sabrina houlihan lokey to double team focused on illiquid sales bloombergcom retrieved    demos telis  houlihan lokey to acquire archpoint partners wall street journal issn  retrieved    demos telis houlihan lokey opens a new front for boutiques consulting retrieved    lang brent  houlihan lokey acquires mesa securities retrieved    houlihan lokey expands consumer food and retail presence in europe with acquisition of londonbased corporate advisory firm mcqueen limited wwwhlcom retrieved    houlihan lokey expands operations in continental europe private equity wire  retrieved    leonardo  houlihan lokey wwwhlcom retrieved    times los angeles houlihan lokey shares rise in trading debut latimescom retrieved    black stone ip  houlihan lokey wwwhlcom retrieved    houlihan lokey information about us ma advisory restructuring financial advisory services wwwhlcom retrieved    houlihan lokey information about us ma advisory restructuring financial advisory services wwwhlcom retrieved    houlihan lokey information about us ma advisory restructuring financial advisory services wwwhlcom retrieved    banker the deals of the year  – americas eceuwestcomputeamazonawscom retrieved    houlihan lokey voices a review of  wwwhlcom retrieved    winners rev